comment: The value of the internal direct product operation, which is a function mapping the (infinite, but finitely supported) cartesian product of subgroups (which mutually commute and have trivial intersections) to its (group) sum . (Contributed by Mario Carneiro, 25-Apr-2016.) (Revised by AV, 11-Jul-2019.)
